data.description: This house is absolutely remarkable! The entire interior has been updated and brought back to life with modern touches that you'll absolutely love. This house is located on a dead-end street on a 0.69-acre lot that welcomes you up to a lovely, covered side porch area. You then are led into the kitchen area with all updated cabinetry, gray subway backsplash, butcher block countertops, ship lap ceiling, stainless appliances and a tile flooring that flows into the dining room. Built ins with a bench offers a cozy sitting area with access to the back yard and patio. The living room has tray ceilings with crown molding, fireplace and carpet, perfect for entertaining. Full bathroom in the main hallway with a tub, tile walls and flooring, glass door and updated vanity. 3 Bedrooms with hardwood flooring, recessed lighting and large closets in each. The basement is partially finished with a living area huddled around the second fireplace with carpet. Small kitchenette for a secondary kitchen area or bar. 1/2 bath. Laundry tucked around the back. Small workshop area. Glass block windows with vents. 1.5 car garage with a shed. Newer water heater. Gas forced air furnace/AC. Vinyl windows. Aluminum siding. 3-tab shingled roof.  100-amp panel. Sump pump. Well and public sewage. Liberty School District or open enrollment option to Girard which is 2 minutes down the road. This house WILL NOT LAST so call today and schedule! BEST AND FINAL OFFERS DUE TONIGHT 4/19/24 9 PM.
